    <!-- Modal Content -->
    <form class="modal-content animate">
        <div class="fappy_container">
            <h1 class="text-center">Wallin Farms</h1>
            <div class="text-center">
                <img src="/Images/WallinFarmsField.jpg" alt="Photo of tractor disking a field" style="width:75%">
            </div>
            <h2>Description:</h2>
            <p>
                <i>November 2020 - January 2021</i>
                <br /><br />
                I registered corn tickets and invoices into Excel spreadsheets to look for discrepancies between actual prices
                and what the prices should be.
                <br /><br />
                <i>March - August 2020</i>
                <br /><br />
                I fixed tires, gearboxes, and center drives on irrigation pivots in corn fields. I strip tilled corn fields by operating a tractor.
